# /etc/nftables/mullvad-endpoints.nft — SEED (no-op).
# The mullvad_wg set is declared (empty) inside host-backstop.nft, so this
# file only needs to exist for the include to succeed before the first
# refresh. refresh-mullvad-endpoints.sh overwrites it with real endpoints.
# (An empty interval set cannot be written as `{ }`, so we add nothing here.)
